  <sect2 role="package">
    <title>Introduction to SBC</title>

    <para>
      The <application>SBC</application> is a digital audio encoder and decoder used to
      transfer data to Bluetooth audio output devices like headphones or loudspeakers.
    </para>

    &lfs91_checked;

